  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764607348\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764607348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764607348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/2c245d791114e8c40dd1699b0ee7c1e2.avif?t=1764607348\" width=610 height=246 /></span><br>Black ido is a super suit that can change gravity and protect the main character named TSK from falling from a great height.  <br><br>Feature of game:  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure with the change of gravity  <br></li><li>Collecting coins <br></li><li>Convenient control <br></li><li>Challenging levels <br></li><li>Physics, doors, keys and traps. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/86352909f9e5cfb9e68d53836701d560.poster.avif?t=1764607348\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/86352909f9e5cfb9e68d53836701d560.webm?t=1764607348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474850/extras/86352909f9e5cfb9e68d53836701d560.mp4?t=1764607348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>In the game you have to change the gravity and use the geometry of the level to solve puzzles.",
